Office Equipment Leasing & Financing 
Computers? Storage? Furniture? We’ll custom tailor a lease to help you get down to business — affordably.


 







Home > Industry Specific Leasing & Financing > Office Equipment Leasing & Financing




Leasing for New and Used Office Equipment
Do you have the right equipment to get your business buttoned-down?  Companies, from the smallest mom-and-pop down the street to the world’s largest multi-national firms, all have something in common… the need for dependable, modern and cost-effective office equipment. Having something as basic as the right tools can make the difference between success and bankruptcy. National Funding specializes in office equipment leasing and financing for our nation’s small businesses. Helping you to get the tools and equipment to be able to service your customers is what we do.
Office equipment doesn’t come cheap and constant technological advances may make it difficult to keep up with your competitors. But you can get all the latest tools and equipment you need to stay on the cutting edge, quickly and easily, while retaining your working capital and protecting your cash flow.
National Funding offers leases for both new and used equipment, a real advantage when cost is a consideration.  And because we can custom tailor your lease to your company’s budget, you can invest in needed equipment to achieve your growth potential.  At the same time, by leasing equipment, you’ll earn significant tax benefits while leaving other credit lines open for other needed expenditures.
You’re the business owner, and no one knows your business like you do.  And no one knows leasing like National Funding does.  Let us help you find the right lease for the office equipment that your company needs – replacement, upgrades, expansion. 

 


Types of Business Office Equipment Leasing

Communication Systems
Computers and servers
Copiers
Filing / Storage
Furniture / Fixtures
Hardware
Mailing Equipment
Mobile Computing
Printers & Printing Equipment
Refrigerators, stoves, and storage
Servers & IT Equipment
Software


 




We Can Help Lease Office Equipment to Grow Your Business
No one knows your business and its potential as well as you.   We’re here to help you realize that potential with sound and practical equipment leasing solutions that meet your needs and exceed your expectations. Regardless of the size of your business, National Funding has the expertise to help you finance or lease the office equipment you need to grow your business.

 



