Equipment Finance



















































Equipment Finance
CIT Equipment Finance works directly with small business, middle market companies, and government entities to deliver commercial finance solutions for the acquisition of equipment and value-added services. We also work with manufacturers, distributors, resellers, dealers and systems integrators to create financing programs for their commercial customers.  

Products & Services
Capital equipment financing Finance programs for equipment manufacturersFinance programs for franchisorsDirect to end user finance offerings to commercial entities


Our Businesses
Equipment Finance   - Works with manufacturers, franchisors, distributors, resellers, dealers and systems integrators to finance their equipment, software and services to commercial customers. Small ticket transactions are typically between $25,000 and $50,000 while mid-ticket deals start at $250,000.Capital Equipment Finance  - Works directly with middle market and large cap businesses to help finance their capital equipment needs. Typical transactions are over $3 million.Direct Capital  - Works directly with small businesses to help lease or finance equipment through a highly automated credit approval, documentation and funding process. Typical transactions are under $1 million, but may be larger.



































