Leasing funds


        
    

Macquarie Equipment Leasing Fund
Macquarie Asset Management Inc. is the manager of Macquarie Equipment Leasing Fund, LLC (MELF).
MELF provides individual US investors with access to the global equipment leasing, deal origination, asset management, equipment remarketing and funds management expertise of the Macquarie Group.
