       Investments in Macquarie Equipment Leasing Fund, LLC are not deposits with or other liabilities of Macquarie Bank Limited ABN 46 008 583 542, or of any entity in the Macquarie Group and are subject to investment risk , including possible delays in repayment and loss of income and capital invested. Neither Macquarie Bank Limited nor any other member company of the Macquarie Group guarantees any particular rate of return or the performance of the Macquarie Equipment Leasing Fund, LLC nor do they guarantee the repayment of capital from Macquarie Equipment Leasing Fund, LLC.
    

       This website is neither an offer to sell nor the solicitation of an offer to buy any security. Only the prospectus can make such an offer. Therefore, a copy of the prospectus must be made available to you in connection with the offering. This advertising material must be read in conjunction with the prospectus in order to understand fully all of the implications and risks of the offering of securities to which it relates. Because it is a summary, it may not contain all of the information that is important to you. To understand the Macquarie Equipment Leasing Fund offering fully, you should read the entire prospectus and Risk Factors carefully, including the "Questions and Answers About this Offering" and "Risk Factors" sections and the financial statements, before making a decision to invest in our shares. Some of the more significant risks include the following: lack of operating history and "blind pool" nature of the offering; less diversification if we do not raise substantially more than the minimum offering; absence of public market for the shares and lack of liquidity; dependence on our manager and its affiliates; conflicts of interest among us and our manager and its affiliates; and a substantial portion of distributions received from us may be a return of capital rather than a return on capital. We cannot assure you that we will achieve any of our investment objectives. Use of this website is subject to its Important Information and Privacy Policy.
    





 

