Equipment leasing






Equipment leasing








Equipment leasing


        
    




       Macquarie Asset Management Inc. (MAMI)
    

       Benefits of Leasing
    

       Corporations and governments routinely turn to lease financing as a preferred method of equipment acquisition. Leasing can provide benefits which include:
    





              Conservation of working capital
            

              Off-balance sheet financing
            

              Tailored terms and payments
            

              Avoidance of expenditure spikes
            





              Preservation of debt facilities
            

              Tax advantages
            

              Streamlined budgeting
            

              Protection against obsolescence
            





       Equipment Types
    

       Our global equipment leasing services cover a variety of different types of equipment, including the following equipment types:
    





              Aeronautical
            

              Rail
            

              Utilities
            

              Mining
            

              Semiconductor
            

              Telecommunications
            

              Medical
            





              Maritime
            

              Road Transportation
            

              Construction
            

              Manufacturing
            

              Information Technology
            

              Scientific
            

              Other Equipment Types
            





       Tailored and flexible leasing structures are available.
    

       Further Information
    

       For more information about our equipment leasing services, please contact us.
    

        
    











