Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Specialty Finance
Sub-Industry: Commercial Finance
Macquarie Equipment Leasing Fund Two LLC is an investment vehicle that will make investments in equipment and equipment leases. The Company may also make investments in other equipment related transactions which will allow the company to directly or indirectly participate in the benefits and risks of equipment ownership or usage.




