Home > Industry Specific Leasing & Financing > Construction and Contractor Equipment Leasing & Financing




Do You Have the Right Equipment for Your Construction Industry Business?
Having the right tools for the job can make all the difference when it comes to winning a bid. National Funding specializes in financing and leasing equipment for the construction industry. Helping you to get the tools and equipment to be able to provide competitive bids and win more business is what we do.
Construction equipment doesn’t come cheap. But you can get all the tools and equipment you need, quickly and easily, while saving your working capital and protecting your cash flow.
With the flexibility to lease new or pre-owned equipment, our custom-tailored construction financing helps you to achieve the stability and growth your business is capable of. Plus, leasing construction equipment protects your credit lines while making it possible to take advantage of huge potential tax savings.
 



No Matter the Size, We Lease Equipment That Can Build Your Business
No one knows your business and its potential as well as you. We’re here to help you realize that potential with sound and practical equipment lease solutions for the construction industry that meet your needs and exceed your expectations.  From large construction firms and general contractors to finish carpenters, electricians, and plumbers, National Funding has the expertise to help you finance and lease the equipment you need to lay a foundation of success for your business.
 Apply today and take the first step toward securing the construction equipment financing and leasing that you need to improve your operational efficiency and bottom-line results.

 


